ed all the Arabic words and senses on this page natively developed from سَطَا (saṭā, “to throw oneself upon someone or something with impetuosity; to be restive; to march with large steps; to be found in abundance (said of water)”)."}, "ipa": ["/sawtˤ/"], "lanes_definition": {"source": "lanes", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n21236", "headword_ar": "سَوْطٌ", "root": "swT", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A whip;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a certain thing,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, M,) namely,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "plaited skin,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Bd in lxxxix. 12,) [or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a lash,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "with which one beats,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "strikes,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, M,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "well known;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "i. q."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "miqoraEapN", "text_ar": "مِقْرَعَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (K:) so called because it mixes the flesh with the blood (IDrd, M, K) when a man or a beast is struck with it; (IDrd, TA;) or because its several component parts are mixed together: (Bd, ubi suprà:) pl. [of pauc.]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^asowaATN", "text_ar": "اَسْوَاطٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and [of mult.]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "siyaATN", "text_ar": "سِيَاطٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (S, M, Msb, K:) the latter originally"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "siwaATN", "text_ar": "سِوَاطٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) The saying"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Darabotu zayodFA sawoTFA", "text_ar": "ضَرَبْتُ زَيْدًا سَوْطًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "means"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Darabotu zayodFA bisawoTK", "text_ar": "ضَرَبْتُ زَيْدًا بِسَوْطٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en